snippet.title: 🏴‍☠️Johnny Depp - Victim or Narcissistic Perpetrator?
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp - Victim or Narcissistic Perpetrator?
Disclaimer - I've been a long term fan of Johnny Depp (since 21 Jump Street) and I never even heard of Amber Heard. But now am intrigued with the fall out from their messy marriage and ugly divorce. 
Confused about who to believe? Amber Heard or Johnny Depp? 
Me too. This is why I am researching the topic of Reactive Abuse. Who is the abuser here? Is Johnny actually the Narcissist here?
✨THE NARC FREE CHALLENGE ✨ http://bit.ly/2Jx4jB1 
BLOG - https://narcfreeformula.wordpress.com
DONATE: paypal.me/TheWoundedHealer
FACEBOOK https://www.facebook.com/NarcFreeFormula
TWITTER https://twitter.com/free_narc

Relationship DRAMA? Confused about Narcissism? Are they a Narcissist? Psychopath? Not sure but really need to know? Just need to talk to someone about it?  
I offer 1 on 1 consults and will help you clarify what your dealing with and what you plan on doing next. http://bit.ly/NarcFree
I get it - its confusing and scary - but this is IMPORTANT stuff to know.  
Think Chris Watts, Ted Bundy, Charles Manson. I could go on but you get it.
 My name is Freedom and I am a Narc survivor and Indie Author & Consultant. 
Believe me - with my marriage to a Sociopath and working in Community Health for over a decade and subsequent three years independent research in NPD and APD - I KNOW NARCS. 
Let's talk 1 on 1? 
To make a booking:  http://bit.ly/NarcFree
For more info narcfreeformula@gmail.com with the word INFO on the subject matter line. 
Or you can text 0412 222 874 (or from outside Australia 061 412 222 874) and we can schedule a time to talk via mobile or skype.

FREE EBOOK - Narc Free Formula Terminology Booklet. 
When I first stumbled into the world of Narcs, Sociopaths & Psychopaths I was just so relieved to learn there were actually words to explain what I’d been living through. But then I realized how much I needed to know and I gotta say it feels like you’re learning a whole new language at times. 
So, I compiled this list of commonly used Narc phrases or words to help survivors understand “Narc speak”. 

For your free copy, follow these two steps:
1) Email me at NarcFreeFormula@gmail.com
2) In the subject line put the words: Narc Free Formula Terminology Booklet.

ALL CONTRIBUTORS WILL BE CREDITED
